{"tid":1993950,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"Hi喇星,今日打飛機射拎錯人","createTime":"2020-04-29T06:42:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-29T08:05:48.000Z","uid":66987,"like":7,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1fd1e0ce54af08b44123d9a2d030f5746f6a91da","tid":1993950,"uid":66987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:42:39.000Z","msg":"是咁的<br />\n<br />\n平時一大早起身見到梁德明<br />\n<br />\n我已經&quot;動L&quot;左既小弟弟就想向佢發炮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但為求對小明既尊重<br />\n<br />\n於是我特登谷左五日唔打飛機<br />\n<br />\n諗住一炮過射俾小明俾佢做facial<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n今日已經谷左五日如箭在弦既小弟弟再忍唔住啦<br />\n<br />\n一開電視，小明已經係到ready 緊我d面部護理&quot;精&quot;華&quot;液&quot;<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我用手將小弟弟好似shotgun咁狂chok<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n就黎顏射佢既時候...你老母<br />\n<br />\n電視突然轉左做林鄭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n我幾億精兵又忍唔住出左一半，收唔撚番<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n於是一路嗌：哎呀，仆街啦，你老母，呀...呀...呀...呀...呀...<br />\n<br />\n就咁我幾億子彈射左落林鄭塊面到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n仆街，而家仲好撚興<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ，早知下次定住個畫面先射<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n還番我谷左五個禮拜既精兵俾我呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2cdd6e035b04823a1de28911ec0929ffb3bb7a48","tid":1993950,"uid":66987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T06:47:39.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/lick.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9c2e7512924a4deecaa25aa5b4430cee9fa607c3","tid":1993950,"uid":66987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:20:15.000Z","msg":"推<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a37d65397a9ea0439aa25ada3e8f9d6546e9c149","tid":1993950,"uid":105343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:38:39.000Z","msg":"嗯"},{"pid":"de7fde155e98be4482a0ddf1fb4d456fce3f1bba","tid":1993950,"uid":246588,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T07:39:47.000Z","msg":"屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04623c5af614948472834bd1cc0737b80612e32b","tid":1993950,"uid":66987,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T08:04:27.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"02dea85a6c34fc69046a98fb9c971237d2c6493c","tid":1993950,"uid":51039,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-29T08:05:48.000Z","msg":"五日定五個禮拜"}]}